    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/28b25205e9bb3871b6e50288cb27112e.poster.avif?t=1771603041\" width=1266 height=634 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/28b25205e9bb3871b6e50288cb27112e.webm?t=1771603041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/28b25205e9bb3871b6e50288cb27112e.mp4?t=1771603041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEND AGAINST THE HEROES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An army of valiant heroes is invading. Assemble a team of monsters and tactically position them to defend against the onslaught. Battle against increasingly difficult waves of enemies across 8 handcrafted stages with over 40 monsters to choose from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/d52209e86f5a2d90c1a1b1cbe663966d.poster.avif?t=1771603041\" width=1218 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/d52209e86f5a2d90c1a1b1cbe663966d.webm?t=1771603041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/d52209e86f5a2d90c1a1b1cbe663966d.mp4?t=1771603041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>ASSEMBLE YOUR TEAM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fine-tune your team in the Hollow Road, a safe-haven between stages. Here you can add or remove monsters from your deck and purchase powerful artifacts. Use these tools to streamline your strategy and unlock powerful synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/528cdf59f7796331d623b80be574478b.poster.avif?t=1771603041\" width=514 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/528cdf59f7796331d623b80be574478b.webm?t=1771603041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/528cdf59f7796331d623b80be574478b.mp4?t=1771603041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNLOCK BOOSTER PACKS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock 13+ booster packs. Booster packs offer a new way to start your runs, adding different monsters to the starting deck, keeping things fresh and enabling you to try different strategies. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/bf91ab4dbf325727be79424f309fe74c.apng?t=1771603041\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336250/extras/bf91ab4dbf325727be79424f309fe74c.poster.avif?t=1771603041\" class=\"bb_img\" width=312 height=48 /></picture></span></h2>",
